%S A395878 1,1,3,19,105,763,5766,46283,383254,3265855
%N A395878 Number of oriented polyominoes in the {6,4} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%C A395878 For oriented polyominoes, chiral pairs are counted as two.
%H A395878 <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/PF-Non-Euclidean">Wiki page indexing sequences related to non-euclidean polyforms</a>
%F A395878 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of oriented {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q. In this case, P{p,oo} = A221184.
%t A395878 (* Cf. A394862 with p=6 and q=4. *)
%Y A395878 Cf. A221184, A393729, A394862.
%K A395878 nonn,more
